metadata.name: Fritzi
metadata.description:
Each Block Queen has her own unique, strong personality. She can't, and won't, be tamed. Experience each Queen in her full glory by interacting with the piece. Dive in deep, explore every layer, and find what makes her truly one-of-a-kind.

[View Fullscreen](https://cowart.mypinata.cloud/ipfs/QmdtxqZHXF2Z9k8oiDKMLi3zySLECjyWZ2o8DverUfVhu5/1.html)  
[View Cover](https://cowart.mypinata.cloud/ipfs/QmNaYTV3j97h9DLLLiyxFLDgqn9a78KCeV8saHEULTMLnB/1.png)

Created by Jeremy Cowart  
Powered by Transient Labs

Desktop Experience:  
Left click to rotate. Right click to pan. Scroll to zoom. Shift + S to screenshot.

Mobile Experience:  
Single finger drag to rotate. Two finger drag to pan. Pinch to zoom.
